                    <h2>PSTAnalyzerr </h2>

                    <h3>SIS2014/2015@FOI</h3>

                    <p>
                        TASK: Create a software for reading emails from PST file, analyzes it's data (from, to, cc, bcc,
                        subject and content). There is requirement for full-text search in emails. UI allows search for
                        each email by it's content, from, to, subject... Show emails for given period of time and count
                        them for each person. Main goal is to graphicaly show connection between senders and recievers
                        inside PST file.<br><br>
                        Project is still in the development phase.
                    </p>

                    <h3>How to use application:</h3>
                    <ol>
                        <li> After application has started, choose PST file.</li>
                        <li>Press "Launch" button</li>
                        <li> After PST file is analyzed (can take up to a few minutes depending on
                            file size), open web browser with address: http://localhost:4567/
                        </li>
                    </ol>

